star, and US Department of the Treasury.  aTitle from PDF title page (viewed on October 25, 2014).  a4420aCoca-Cola CompanyxAccounting. 0aCash flowxAccountingvCase studies. 0aFinance and financial management collection.x2331-0057403University of Alberta Accessuhttp://site.ebrary.com/lib/ualbertagep/Doc?id=10956092  hUAINzEBRARYBEP  aInternet AccesswLCc1i6741149-1001lINTERNETmUAINTERNETrYsYtE-RESOURCEu11/21/2014xE-BOOKzEBRARYBEP01ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n80020347